Step 1 - Open power bi report
Step 2 - Import 'Histogram chart' visual in the power bi report.
To import 'Histogram chart', go to Visualization pane -> Click on three dots -> Get more visuals -> Search 'Histogram' -> Add 'Histogram chart'

Step 3 - Add 'Histogram chart' visual in the power bi report.
To add 'Histogram chart', go to Visualization pane -> Drag and drop 'Histogram chart' visual in Power BI report.

Step 4 - Add fields into the 'Histogram chart' visual
Put 'Marks' in the values field.

In this way, we can make and use Histogram charts in the power bi report.
